 Notice on the sail:  Attorney for you available

3
00:01:16,290 --> 00:01:19,834
 The spirit who dies unjustly wanders in the afterlife,

4
00:01:19,834 --> 00:01:24,854
 harms a living person, or causes natural disasters.

5
00:01:26,167 --> 00:01:30,094
 Aristocrats, commoners, and slaves

6
00:01:30,094 --> 00:01:32,764
 are all equal only within the law.

7
00:01:32,764 --> 00:01:37,984
 The people complain of injustice to the monarch through petitions.

8
00:01:37,984 --> 00:01:44,294
 There are individuals who help ignorant people who can neither read nor know the law.

9
00:01:44,294 --> 00:01:48,454
 They are called attorneys.

10
00:01:55,174 --> 00:01:57,854
Good, good, good.

11
00:01:57,854 --> 00:02:00,834
We finally arrived in Hanyang.

12
00:02:01,794 --> 00:02:03,534
What are you going to do now?

13
00:02:03,534 --> 00:02:06,844
We need to set up an attorney's office.

14
00:02:06,844 --> 00:02:11,654
You spent all the money you saved in the country to buy this boat.

15
00:02:11,654 --> 00:02:13,984
Who comes to Hanyang without a single story?

16
00:02:13,984 --> 00:02:17,834
Who leaves Hanyang without a single story?

17
00:02:19,674 --> 00:02:21,204
Don't you understand?

18
00:02:21,204 --> 00:02:25,384
All I see is my cash cow.

19
00:02:25,384 --> 00:02:28,294
This is the best place for business.

20
00:02:30,674 --> 00:02:34,024
But what is the place you are talking about?

21
00:02:35,634 --> 00:02:36,700
Here!

22
00:02:37,594 --> 00:02:40,684
Pardon? Here?

23
00:02:41,444 --> 00:02:44,074
It even smells different.

24
00:02:44,714 --> 00:02:47,664
It smells f-fishy.

25
00:02:50,514 --> 00:02:53,704
I love this Hanyang smell so much.

26
00:03:02,464 --> 00:03:07,764
 Episode 1: Attorney Kang Han Su

27
00:03:07,764 --> 00:03:12,260
 Joseon Attorney

28
00:03:15,114 --> 00:03:17,214
Please buy gat (hats for men). Gat!

