Kang Han Su?

229
00:22:27,234 --> 00:22:28,784
 What?

230
00:22:29,644 --> 00:22:32,704
We will definitely win. I'm Kang Han Su, the best attorney in Joseon.

231
00:22:32,704 --> 00:22:34,704
Despicable guy.

232
00:22:38,884 --> 00:22:40,694
Who was it?

233
00:22:40,694 --> 00:22:43,524
Hyeongnim! Hyeongnim!

234
00:22:44,574 --> 00:22:46,874
We are in trouble!

235
00:22:46,874 --> 00:22:48,444
Why?

236
00:22:48,444 --> 00:22:51,874
Park must be planning to leave Hanyang.

237
00:22:51,874 --> 00:22:55,114
He is packing now.

238
00:22:57,764 --> 00:23:00,134
W-Wait...

239
00:23:00,134 --> 00:23:02,034
Wait...

240
00:23:02,034 --> 00:23:04,034
Hurry up!

241
00:23:09,414 --> 00:23:13,474
 Your Excellency, this is Eunuch Go.

242
00:23:24,514 --> 00:23:28,340
Your Excellency, the king is looking for you.

243
00:23:29,914 --> 00:23:34,664
I have an urgent meeting, so let him know I will visit him as soon as this is done.

244
00:23:39,504 --> 00:23:41,424
Y-Yes.

245
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:46,370
 Order

246
00:23:51,224 --> 00:23:55,674
Then I will turn this agenda over to the Ministry of Justice.

247
00:25:07,514 --> 00:25:09,400
It is burning well.

248
00:25:10,544 --> 00:25:12,484
It will burn everything down.

249
00:25:21,367 --> 00:25:24,624
Fire! Fire!

250
00:25:24,624 --> 00:25:26,944
Fire! It is fire!

251
00:25:26,944 --> 00:25:29,574
Aigoo. It is fire!

252
00:25:29,574 --> 00:25:33,154
- Aigoo. Aigoo.
 - Fire!

253
00:25:39,944 --> 00:25:42,364
Mother!

254
00:25:42,364 --> 00:25:45,314
Honey! What should we do?

255
00:25:45,314 --> 00:25:47,784
Oh, what should we do?

256
00:25:50,424 --> 00:25:52,374
Are you all right?

257
00:25:57,044 --> 00:26:01,074
How do we live now? This precious thing is...

