Huh?

676
01:07:57,274 --> 01:07:59,014
What the hell?

677
01:08:03,974 --> 01:08:06,744
Are you awake now?

678
01:08:06,744 --> 01:08:09,794
W-W-Wait! Hey, hey!

679
01:08:09,794 --> 01:08:12,684
Hey! Dong Chi! Damn it!

680
01:08:17,494 --> 01:08:19,634
Here we go again.

681
01:08:19,634 --> 01:08:21,764
Merchant Jang?

682
01:08:21,764 --> 01:08:26,454
Since you recognize me, I guess you know what is about to happen now.

683
01:08:26,454 --> 01:08:28,654
Of course.

684
01:08:30,414 --> 01:08:32,634
- You laugh? 
- What took you so long, Merchant Jang?

685
01:08:32,634 --> 01:08:37,024
I thought my neck was going to give.

686
01:08:37,024 --> 01:08:38,854
What did you say?

687
01:08:39,624 --> 01:08:42,924
By chance, did you have business to take care of with me from the start?

688
01:08:42,924 --> 01:08:46,844
If not for that, there is no reason I would be here,

689
01:08:46,844 --> 01:08:50,574
hanging like this, right?

690
01:09:19,104 --> 01:09:21,084
Merchang Jang.

691
01:09:22,544 --> 01:09:26,754
 Arrest all the family and search throughout the house!

692
01:09:26,754 --> 01:09:28,434
 Yes, Sir!

693
01:09:29,334 --> 01:09:32,004
Should we make a deal?

694
01:09:32,004 --> 01:09:34,624
I will let you live.

695
01:09:38,094 --> 01:09:40,254
Who is going to save whom?

696
01:09:40,254 --> 01:09:43,814
I said I will...

697
01:09:47,654 --> 01:09:51,684
save you. Okay? Okay?

698
01:09:51,684 --> 01:09:54,354
Geez! Wait, wait, wait! Hey!

699
01:09:54,354 --> 01:09:58,494
I am talking to you! You are dead!

